{
  "stem": "18102.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When, when I began to give lectures on financial matters in Japan, and when, as chairman of the Chicago Mercantile Exchange, we opened a permanent office in Tokyo, and I travel to Japan quite often, I, of course, became very conscious of the fact that Japan had an affinity to me that was different than everyone else.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Here I was, alive, and a leader of finance in the United States, by virtue of the fact that once, some years ago, a Japanese gentleman gave me this opportunity, as a child, to survive.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I began, in my speeches, to talk about this event to many crowds in the financial arena of Japan.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I would say to them, you know, I am a survivor of the Holocaust simply because a gentleman named Sugihara saved my life-- and this was of great interest in a introduction of a speech, you can imagine, on financial matters, when I'm talking about one of their own.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I used that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As a consequence of that, people began to write that story and write what I was saying in the news.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I would get interviewed, and so my connection began to grow stronger and stronger, as it related to Sugihara.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I know, definitely, it was in the middle '70s that it began, because that was then that we begin to, as the Chicago Mercantile Exchange, become international.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we moved into connection to Japan.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so my first actual foray as a speaker was with the Nobel laureate in economics, my good friend Milton Friedman, who invited me to, to share a stage with him, which was a great honor in itself, and speak about future markets.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was the beginning, and it began in the middle to late '70s.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
